1
00:00:00,780 --> 00:00:03,340
Oh, I love snow!
哦   我超爱下雪

2
00:00:03,350 --> 00:00:05,160
I love snow, too!
我也爱死了

3
00:00:05,940 --> 00:00:11,120
Careful, Humf. It might be slippery. Let's all hold hands.
小心点  Humf  下了雪会很滑的   我们都牵着手吧

4
00:00:14,660 --> 00:00:15,700
Oops!
哎哟

5
00:00:16,380 --> 00:00:17,960
My mitten!
我的手套

6
00:00:18,300 --> 00:00:22,600
Oh, dear, you need to keep your mittens on, Humf.
哦   亲爱的   你得戴上手套哦    Humf

7
00:00:22,610 --> 00:00:25,040
Or you'll have very cold hands.
不然你的手会很冷

8
00:00:25,740 --> 00:00:28,480
It was funny to walk in the snow.
雪中行走真有趣

9
00:00:29,040 --> 00:00:33,720
Everywhere they stepped, they left foot shapes behind them.
他们一迈步子   后面就会留下脚印

10
00:00:42,920 --> 00:00:46,220
More snow was falling down from the sky.
雪不停地从天空飘落

11
00:00:46,760 --> 00:00:51,760
It fell tickly on Humf's nose and it made him blink his eyes.
雪顽皮地落在Humf的鼻子上   弄得他直眨眼睛

